{
  "stem": "24884.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we met-- you mean after the-- when the Nazis started in '33?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was-- that was already after 1933.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we had friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stuck together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We-- we had a fairly normal life until 1937, '38. '37, yeah. '38.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went swimming, and we went to the beach.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we went and visited each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had little home parties.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Berlin is a city with lots of water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was Wannsee, the Little Wannsee, the Big Wannsee.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, a lot of beaches.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember once that I went to a theater to saw a-- and I saw At-- I think at the [GERMAN], or some kind of [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had like a daily German newspaper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I don't even recall what kind of papers we had or any-- I was too young for that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very limited.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very little.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By seeing it, by experiencing it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that we were then forbidden to go into a movie.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were forbidden to go to the beach.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were to-- forbidden to do almost anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were singled out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there were announcements.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were in the papers, and over the radio.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there-- there must have been a Jewish paper where all the laws were printed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I was aware of.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they-- I-- in the beginning, it was possible because you didn't have to wear the Star of David.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you took a chance to use a subway, or to do this or-- you know, you-- you didn't get caught immediately all the time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But once you-- I don't even remember when that was.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
